flowchart TD
    Req[/HTTP Request to ChartController/] --> Router{Which endpoint?}

    Router -->|POST monthly| Monthly[ChartController.monthly<br/>ServerWebExchange + MDHChartRequest]
    Router -->|POST daily| Daily[ChartController.daily<br/>ServerWebExchange + DailySKRequest]
    Router -->|POST hourly| Hourly[ChartController.hourly<br/>ServerWebExchange + HourlySKRequest]
    Router -->|POST bill-explainer| Bill[ChartController.billExplainer<br/>ServerWebExchange + BillExplainer.SK.Request]

    Monthly --> SvcMonthly[ChartService.retrieveMonthly]
    Daily --> MapDaily[BDLChart.Daily.Request.getDailyRequestForGraph<br/>map SK to BDL request]
    MapDaily --> SvcDaily[ChartService.retrieveDaily]
    Hourly --> MapHourly[BDLChart.Hourly.Request.getHourlyRequestForGraph<br/>map SK to BDL request]
    MapHourly --> SvcHourly[ChartService.retrieveHourly]
    Bill --> SvcBill[ChartService.retrieveBillExplainer]

    SvcMonthly --> JarvisMonthly[Jarvis Chart API<br/>monthly MDH endpoint]
    JarvisMonthly --> JarvisMonthlyCheck{Jarvis call OK?}
    JarvisMonthlyCheck -->|success| MonthlyResp[/200 MDHChartResponse<br/>premiseType + monthly data/]
    JarvisMonthlyCheck -->|failure| MonthlyErr[/ChartApiException<br/>CHART_MONTHLY_JARVIS_ERROR/]

    SvcDaily --> JarvisDaily[Jarvis Chart API<br/>daily BDL endpoint]
    JarvisDaily --> JarvisDailyCheck{Jarvis call OK?}
    JarvisDailyCheck -->|success| DailyResp[/200 BDLChart Daily Response/]
    JarvisDailyCheck -->|failure| DailyErr[/ChartApiException<br/>CHART_DAILY_JARVIS_ERROR/]

    SvcHourly --> JarvisHourly[Jarvis Chart API<br/>hourly BDL endpoint]
    JarvisHourly --> JarvisHourlyCheck{Jarvis call OK?}
    JarvisHourlyCheck -->|success| HourlyResp[/200 BDLChart Hourly Response/]
    JarvisHourlyCheck -->|failure| HourlyErr[/ChartApiException<br/>CHART_HOURLY_JARVIS_ERROR/]

    SvcBill --> TariffLookup[(Redis: TariffRepository<br/>lookup tariff data)]
    TariffLookup --> TariffCheck{Tariff cache hit?}
    TariffCheck -->|miss| SchedulerLoad[TariffScheduler refresh<br/>load latest tariff]
    SchedulerLoad --> SapCall[SAP Backend API<br/>via SAPService]
    TariffCheck -->|hit| SapCall
    SapCall --> SapCheck{SAP returned data?}
    SapCheck -->|success| BillResp[/200 BillExplainer Response/]
    SapCheck -->|failure| BillErr[/ChartApiException<br/>BILL_EXPLAINER_ERROR/]

    MonthlyErr --> ErrHandler[Reactive error handler<br/>onErrorResume]
    DailyErr --> ErrHandler
    HourlyErr --> ErrHandler
    BillErr --> ErrHandler
    ErrHandler --> Resp5xx[/5xx error JSON response/]
